Contact Us

HealthSouth Corporate Office
3660 Grandview Parkway, Suite 200
Birmingham, AL 35243
(205) 967-7116 
Find a Location
Please direct all hospital specific questions and comments to the HealthSouth facility closest to you. Try our Hospital Locator to get started.
HealthSouth Careers
If you have any questions regarding applying for a job or the status of your application, please contact a recruiter within your region. To view available positions and apply, search for jobs in the Careers section of our site.
Becoming a HealthSouth Partner
If you are considering options on post-acute care or participating in the healthcare reform models, let us talk to you. We can offer a free, no-obligation analysis of your current inpatient rehabilitation unit or hospital and give you feedback on opportunities we see for growth or improvement. If you do not currently offer inpatient rehabilitation services, but feel there is a need in your community, we would be happy to provide a market analysis for your review. If you would like more information about partnering with HealthSouth, or would like to schedule a meeting, please call 205 969 8268 or e-mail us at partnership@healthsouth.com.
Becoming a HealthSouth Vendor
HealthSouth partners with a diverse supplier base that offer products or services that meet the needs of a large integrated delivery network of inpatient rehabilitation hospitals across the country.  HealthSouth focuses on utilizing our Group Purchasing Organization, MedAssets, for most supply-related contracts. The MedAssets program offers contracting opportunities with manufacturers, distributors and service providers that are certified as minority-owned, female-owned, veteran-owned and small disadvantaged-owned businesses. HealthSouth also aims to work with suppliers that can handle electronic transactions to improve the control and compliance of our supply-related expenses.  If you are interested in partnering with HealthSouth, please click here to go to the MedAssets website and apply to be their supplier or email feedback@healthsouth.com to gain more information on HealthSouth’s needs.
Click here to go to the MedAssets website and apply.
Investor Relations
Visit our investor relations site to view our company profile, stock information, news and more.
Media Hotline
Members of the media requesting information or an interview can call (205) 410-2777.
Questions
Visit our Frequently Asked Questions section, or use the form below to contact us.












