Who We Are
HealthSouth is dedicated to being the best in rehabilitation and being the best means hiring the best. HealthSouth nurses, therapists, pharmacists, home health care specialists and other professionals are united in making a real difference.
Click to Learn More About Who We Are







Benefits
At HealthSouth, we continually strive to provide high-quality, comprehensive benefits to our valued employees. That includes working to balance the rising costs of benefits with the growing needs of the HealthSouth team.
Click to Learn More About Benefits







Recruiting Events
Staying at the forefront of rehabilitation means we never stop looking for talented people to join our team. We have a strong presence at conferences and career fairs with national rehabilitation associations. Our individual hospitals attend local job fairs, coordinate “lunch-and-learn” events at local colleges and host open house staffing events. Check this page often for an updated calendar. Chances are we’ll be hosting an event near you. We would love to get to know you.
Click to Learn More About Recruiting Events







 



